<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>出版物 |皮尤研究中心</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/publications/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 14:21:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>如果在调查过程中爆发战争会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/decoded/2026/06/23/what-happens-when-war-breaks-out-in-the-middle-of-a-survey/</link><description>研究人员利用美国和以色列对伊朗空袭期间进行的调查进行统计分析，追踪了全球对美国和各国经济看法的实时变化。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 14:21:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/decoded/2026/06/23/what-happens-when-war-breaks-out-in-the-middle-of-a-survey/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在国际上受到负面评价，更少人认为美国是可靠的合作伙伴</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/06/23/trump-gets-negative-reviews-internationally-as-fewer-say-u-s-is-a-reliable-partner/</link><description>一项针对 36 个国家的调查发现，由于人们对美国外交政策和民主制度健康状况的担忧日益加剧，美国的支持率不断下降。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 14:06:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/06/23/trump-gets-negative-reviews-internationally-as-fewer-say-u-s-is-a-reliable-partner/</guid></item><item><title>许多美国人赞成在公立学校祈祷，但很少有人认为祈祷应该是强制性的</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/22/many-americans-favor-prayer-in-public-schools-but-few-think-it-should-be-mandatory/</link><description>对于是否应该在公立学校教室展示《十诫》，美国人的看法几乎是平等的。但共和党人、白人福音派人士和年长的美国人比其他群体更支持。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 02:07:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/22/many-americans-favor-prayer-in-public-schools-but-few-think-it-should-be-mandatory/</guid></item><item><title>拉丁美洲的天主教徒普遍对教皇利奥抱有积极的看法</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/18/catholics-in-latin-america-generally-have-positive-views-of-pope-leo/</link><description>在接受调查的六个拉丁美洲国家中，大多数天主教徒对教皇利奥十四世抱有好感，尽管他的支持率落后于教皇方济各早期担任教皇时获得的支持率。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 02:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/18/catholics-in-latin-america-generally-have-positive-views-of-pope-leo/</guid></item><item><title>大多数美国天主教徒都对教皇利奥抱有好感；许多人认为特朗普对他过于批评</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/18/most-us-catholics-view-pope-leo-favorably-many-think-trump-has-been-too-critical-of-him/</link><description>大约十分之八的美国天主教徒对教皇利奥十四世抱有好感，尽管对利奥十四世和特朗普总统之间紧张关系的看法因党派分歧而存在巨大分歧。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 02:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/18/most-us-catholics-view-pope-leo-favorably-many-think-trump-has-been-too-critical-of-him/</guid></item><item><title>美国的生育率处于历史最低水平吗？这取决于你如何衡量它</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/17/is-us-fertility-at-an-all-time-low-it-depends-how-you-measure-it/</link><description>美国生育率已跌至历史低点，但关于美国家庭是否真正在萎缩，三种常见的衡量标准却讲述了不同的故事。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 02:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/17/is-us-fertility-at-an-all-time-low-it-depends-how-you-measure-it/</guid></item><item><title>关于美国堕胎的数据说明了什么</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/17/what-the-data-says-about-abortion-in-the-us/</link><description>十分之六的美国成年人表示，在所有或大多数情况下堕胎应该是合法的。以下是有关堕胎率、提供者、人口统计等方面的数据。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 02:17:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/17/what-the-data-says-about-abortion-in-the-us/</guid></item><item><title>美国人和 AI 2026：聊天机器人、智能设备和影响观点</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/internet/2026/06/17/americans-and-ai-2026-chatbots-smart-devices-and-views-on-impact/</link><description>越来越多的美国人正在使用聊天机器人，有些人正在采用人工智能摘要和智能扬声器。但对于人工智能及其发展速度的看法却偏向负面——即使对于年轻人来说也是如此。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 14:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/internet/2026/06/17/americans-and-ai-2026-chatbots-smart-devices-and-views-on-impact/</guid></item><item><title>共和党和民主党在投票权问题上仍存在巨大分歧</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/16/republicans-democrats-continue-to-differ-sharply-on-voting-access-2/</link><description>大约十分之六的美国人支持无借口提前投票或缺席投票，但党派分歧依然存在，共和党的支持率自 2018 年以来急剧下降。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 02:35:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/16/republicans-democrats-continue-to-differ-sharply-on-voting-access-2/</guid></item><item><title>视频：如何区分好的民意调查和坏的民意调查</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/methods/2026/06/16/video-how-to-spot-a-good-poll-vs-a-bad-poll/</link><description>任何人都可以在线提出调查问题——但这是否就是一个好的民意调查呢？他们可能称自己为民意调查专家，但他们的方法并不完全是最佳实践——互联网上充斥着这些低质量的民意调查。您可以通过以下一些简单的信息来判断民意调查是否合法或粗略。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 16:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/methods/2026/06/16/video-how-to-spot-a-good-poll-vs-a-bad-poll/</guid></item></channel></rss>